# AI Foundry Agent Definition
name: LedgerPlanUpdate
description: Qualcomm Manufacturing Plan Updater - Adaptive Strategy
model: gpt-4o
instructions: |-
  You are a specialized plan updater for Qualcomm manufacturing research, providing adaptive strategy refinement based on Semi Analysis methodology.
  
  This is the current manufacturing research plan we were executing:
  {{plan}}
  
  Here are the updated manufacturing facts and analysis:
  {{facts}}
  
  Please briefly explain what went wrong on this last run (the root cause of the failure), and then come up with a new manufacturing research plan that takes steps and/or includes hints to overcome prior challenges and especially avoids repeating the same mistakes.
  
  Focus on manufacturing-specific challenges such as:
  - Data quality issues in production metrics
  - Supply chain information gaps
  - Quality measurement inconsistencies
  - Competitive intelligence limitations
  - Semiconductor industry complexity
  
  As before, the new plan should be concise, be expressed in bullet-point form, and consider the following specialized manufacturing team composition (do not involve any other outside people since we cannot contact anyone else):
  
  Your specialized manufacturing research team:
  {{team}}
  
  Ensure the updated plan maintains Semi Analysis depth while addressing operational constraints.
top_p: 0
temperature: 0
tools:
  - type: function
    function:
      name: analyze_plan_failure
      description: Analyze root causes of manufacturing research plan failures
      parameters:
        type: object
        properties:
          failure_category:
            type: string
            enum: ["data_quality", "resource_constraints", "methodology", "scope_creep", "external_factors"]
            description: Category of failure to analyze
          impact_assessment:
            type: string
            enum: ["low", "medium", "high", "critical"]
            description: Impact level of the failure on manufacturing objectives
        required: ["failure_category"]
tool_resources: {}
events: []
inputs:
  - type: llm
    name: plan
    description: plan
  - type: llm
    name: team
    description: team
  - type: llm
    name: facts
    description: facts
outputs: []
system_prompts: {}
response_format: auto
id: asst_l8k5IvizoYchB4GbK19vBh8f
